dim light.  At the center of the room is what appears to be a whirling
storm, raging silently before you.  It's faint blue glow gives the room an
eerie tinge, its faint whisperings multiplying with every reverberation from
the stone walls.  Heavy doors of dark wood lead from the room to the north
allowing you to flee this place of dark majesty.  
~
