#4310
Atop the Focus Tower~
You find yourself standing on a windswept platform at the highest point
in the City of Apex.  You can see the buildings and districts spread out
below you like a canvas, stretching towards the horizon in all directions. 
From this point you can see the massive bridges suspended above the city,
arcing over the towering walls of the Inner City, and connecting to the
Shard Towers to the southwest and southeast.  In the distant horizon to the
south, you can see the shores of the Sea of Caliban, and the graceful ships
that cut across its vast depths.  Looking down at the city, several hundred
feet below, you realize that it shall be a long descent.  Fortunately, a
path winds its way around the Focus Tower to the west, sloping downward
gently.  To the north lies the doorway into the focus chamber wherein the
construction of the city forces the Wildgate into stability.  Inside the
chamber lies this plane's entrance to the realms beyond.  
~
