#4311
Base of the Compass Tower~
In the center of a barren plain is the massive Compass Tower, stretching
several hundred yards above your head.  In the distance to the north you can
make out the faint curve of the Sea of Caliban several miles away, and to
the north foothills ring the Black Mountains.  `3Notably,`` you see that an
immense wall has been erected to the south and west, and appears to be under
construction.  It carves a jagged arc across the scenery to the south, it's
watchtowers jutting towards the sky.  This new addition makes you wonder if
there shall soon be someone to bar from entry to the City of Apex.  The oak
double doors to the north provide access to the tower's contents.  
~
